  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Well, this is a bit awkward...</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You get a message from your friend <strong><i>Catherine</i></strong>—turns out she's caught a strange virus that's turning her into a cat! (Don't worry, <strong><i>she'll land on her feet</i></strong>, I promise.)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3478950/extras/a572d2835198172ff105d2ef98a09544.avif?t=1748696048\" width=183 height=250 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3478950/extras/ce7cdf3774929e9d67ef6abfceafddf6.webp?t=1748696048\" width=30 height=165 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3478950/extras/f5bbeca20ac2273d3c881f3c6a5e1bc6.avif?t=1748696048\" width=183 height=250 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Your mission:</strong> round up all their cats and embark on a <strong><i>paw-some</i></strong> and wacky adventure!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3478950/extras/72b52cfa9add79a6c4b17cad9515b976.poster.avif?t=1748696048\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3478950/extras/72b52cfa9add79a6c4b17cad9515b976.webm?t=1748696048\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3478950/extras/72b52cfa9add79a6c4b17cad9515b976.mp4?t=1748696048\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>But beware</i>—cats are experts at escape. They may get away once... or twice... <i>or 6 times</i>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Some kitties are extra picky and won’t budge without their favorite toys or treats—so you will have to <strong><i>purr-suade</i></strong> them by finding what they need!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3478950/extras/2783f4387ab7d6af5cf64eb13855ed5f.poster.avif?t=1748696048\" width=164 height=164 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3478950/extras/2783f4387ab7d6af5cf64eb13855ed5f.webm?t=1748696048\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3478950/extras/2783f4387ab7d6af5cf64eb13855ed5f.mp4?t=1748696048\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3478950/extras/ce7cdf3774929e9d67ef6abfceafddf6.webp?t=1748696048\" width=30 height=165 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3478950/extras/3f16250de9efabb19b078753ee0afafb.poster.avif?t=1748696048\" width=164 height=164 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3478950/extras/3f16250de9efabb19b078753ee0afafb.webm?t=1748696048\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3478950/extras/3f16250de9efabb19b078753ee0afafb.mp4?t=1748696048\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3478950/extras/ce7cdf3774929e9d67ef6abfceafddf6.webp?t=1748696048\" width=30 height=165 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3478950/extras/d78152e3f89c45704f8a6505cf1fc8f2.poster.avif?t=1748696048\" width=164 height=164 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3478950/extras/d78152e3f89c45704f8a6505cf1fc8f2.webm?t=1748696048\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3478950/extras/d78152e3f89c45704f8a6505cf1fc8f2.mp4?t=1748696048\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Features:</i></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 500 cats to discover</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6 unique levels</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An inventory system for extra trinkets to be found </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A lot of silly antics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Puns. A lot of puns.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Have I mentioned cats already?</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
